```plantuml
@startuml BoraxTheClean_DevelopmentMachine
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor Developer

rectangle "GitHub Actions" as GitHubActions #lightsteelblue

rectangle "AWS CloudFormation" as CloudFormation #lightyellow

rectangle "AWS EC2" as EC2 #aliceblue

rectangle "IAM" as IAM #lightgreen

rectangle "CloudWatch" as CloudWatch #mistyrose

' ========== Connections ==========
Developer --> GitHubActions : push changes

' GitHub Actions workflow
GitHubActions -> CloudFormation : package and deploy template
GitHubActions -> S3 : upload template

' CloudFormation template deployment
CloudFormation -> EC2 : create instance
EC2 -> IAM : request credentials
IAM -> EC2 : provide credentials

' CloudWatch alarm for inactivity
EC2 -> CloudWatch : monitor activity
CloudWatch -> EC2 : stop instance after 1 hour inactivity

@enduml
```